  "title": "RESTAURANT SUPERVISOR (5 day work week)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Provide excellent customer service to all guests.</li>\n  <li>Take reservations and enquire purpose of visit.</li>\n  <li>Greet each guest courteously and promptly.</li>\n  <li>Share promotions, specials and items to customers.</li>\n  <li>Take food and beverage orders, repeat orders to guests, inform guest of estimated service time.</li>\n  <li>Oversee a team of servers who are assigned to his/her shift.</li>\n  <li>Efficiently input orders in the Point-of-Sale system.</li>\n  <li>Process payment and check bills promptly.</li>\n  <li>Maintain cleanliness of the outlet.</li>\n  <li>Assist manager by getting involved in planning and organizing of special events.</li>\n  <li>Check food and beverage inventories and stocks in a consistent and accurate manner.</li>\n  <li>Follow Food &amp; Beverage Safety and Hygiene policies and procedures.</li>\n  <li>Complete opening, operating, and closing procedures.</li>\n  <li>Troubleshoot any issues related to cashier payments.</li>\n  <li>Escalate guests feedback to duty manager.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Good command of spoken English</li>\n  <li>Pleasant and outgoing personality</li>\n  <li>Team player, preferable with good communication and interpersonal skills</li>\n  <li>Positive service attitude, coachable</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Able to work on weekends and public holidays</li>\n  <li>5 day work week</li>\n  <li>Variable and daily incentive scheme</li>\n  <li>Free shuttle bus from Tanah Merah MRT station</li>\n</ul>",
